#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn47.33"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.33:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.33:0.2"
msgid "4. Ananussutavagga "
msgstr "4. Not Learned From Anyone Else "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Viraddhasutta "
msgstr "33. Missed Out "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.180, sc1
#. VAR: viraddho tesaṃ ariyo maggo → ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "sn47.33:1.1"
msgid "“Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā viraddhā, viraddho tesaṃ ariyo maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, whoever has missed out on the four kinds of mindfulness meditation has missed out on the noble path to the complete ending of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn47.33:1.2"
msgid "Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā āraddhā, āraddho tesaṃ ariyo maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī. "
msgstr "Whoever has undertaken the four kinds of mindfulness meditation has undertaken the noble path to the complete ending of suffering. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn47.33:2.1"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.5"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.33:2.6"
msgid "Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhānā viraddhā, viraddho tesaṃ ariyo maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī. "
msgstr "Whoever has missed out on these four kinds of mindfulness meditation has missed out on the noble path to the complete ending of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn47.33:2.7"
msgid "Yesaṃ kesañci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhānā āraddhā, āraddho tesaṃ ariyo maggo sammā dukkhakkhayagāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Whoever has undertaken these four kinds of mindfulness meditation has undertaken the noble path to the complete ending of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.33:2.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

